local a={"Ichihime’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Ichihime\n\"Nyaa? Nyanyanya-nya! \"","Beach Party Exclusive\n\"Take this! Even if it\'s you, Master, Ichihime won\'t let you get an easy win-nya!\"","New Year\'s First Visit Exclusive\n\" I\'m busy trying out the food for everybody, of course. This is the most important task-nya!\"","“Cat Warrior Ichihime is here, and a brave and wise person like you is surely my master, nyaa! From now on, I\'ll guard your luck and safety, nyaa~\"","Spring Song Exclusive\n\"Nyaa! Easy peasy! I\'ll handle the lion head, and leave the rear to you, Master! It\'s time to show everyone what we are capable of. As Mahjong Soul Shrine\'s lion dance duo, we will definitely get a Mangan with Ippatsu, nyaa!\"","Freshman Mornings Exclusive\n\"Nyaa! Master, look! The snacks are on super sale, nyaa! And this is my favorite flavor! Master, don\'t you think a good girl who\'s been behaving well in class deserves a treat, nyaa?\"","Miki Nikaidou’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Miki Nikaidou\n\"Sure. I\'m all~ yours~ today.\"","Halloween Party Exclusive\n\"If tonight\'s ball doesn\'t delight you, let me teach you something that will make you happy.\"","Spring Celebration Exclusive\n\"You know, it\'s not nice to sneak a peek while girls are putting on makeup! I want you to see me at my best today!\"","Night of the Iris Exclusive\n\"Tonight\'s banquet is a celebration of success... Oh, you ask for whom? Hehe, of course, for everyone present, including you, my dear {name}. Did you know, that everyone is present tonight because of you?\"","Playful Summertime Exclusive\n\"Hiding there, are you planning to pull me into the water when I\'m not looking? Heehee, if you insist on doing that, I can cooperate a bit and pretend to be scared, letting out the scream you want to hear.\"","Kana Fujita’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Kana Fujita\n\"Let\'s go shopping together again next time. \"","Christmas Carnival Exclusive\n\"Hi everyone! Thanks for coming to Kana\'s Christmas Eve concert. \"","Code of Shadows Exclusive\n\"So you are the one who trespassed into the witch\'s forest, hm? Only those with special powers dare enter this forest, so how about I do some experiment on you to see what your deal is?\"","Beachside Vacation Exclusive\n\"Come with me to celebrate the great success of the concert with ice cream and coconut water! Before we dig in, let me take a photo first... Eh? Gain... weight? Don\'t talk about such horrid things during our date! And... since the concert is over, I get to indulge myself a bit, okay?\"","Echoes of Rejoicing Exclusive\n\"You\'re here early! I\'m still doing my makeup – heehee... But that means the first person Kana sees in the New Year is you, {name}! I love this surprise! Happy New Year! Ah, would you help me with my hairpin? Just gently... You have to treat a girl\'s hair with care, and of course, her feelings too!\"","Chiori Mikami’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Chiori Mikami\nChiori is so cute ！","Christmas Carnival Exclusive\n\"C\'mon... Every Christmas, my room is flooded with Christmas gifts.\"","Beach Party Exclusive\n\"Even a commoner like you can have a great taste sometimes. I... can allow you to take one photo of me. Hmph!\"","Sweet Refreshment Exclusive\n\"It\'s been ten minutes and you still haven\'t decided what to order! Hmph, you\'re not doing this just to stare at my new dress for a little longer, are you? Well, in that case, I\'ll write down every item on the menu for you.\"","Close Your Eyes Exclusive\n\"You, don\'t just stand there looking! Come help me with my outfit... Wh-what, it\'s not because I can\'t do it on my own! You are my servant, so do what servants do, and don\'t make me remind you. Humph, how troublesome!\"","Echoes of Rejoicing Exclusive\n\"Wealth rolling in! Loads of Dora tiles! Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans! Humph, My New Year\'s blessing is just what you wanted, right? You should be gratefully accepting it with utmost reverence. Now hurry up and join me for a match – this is your golden opportunity to make my words come true!\"","Mai Aihara’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Mai Aihara\n\"This dance, \"Kagura\", is dedicated to you only. \"","Beach Party Exclusive\n\"I\'m not particularly good at swimming... But I will try my best. \"","Wonderful Youth Exclusive\n\"I was happy that you could celebrate Lunar New Year with me, so I tried this special outfit. Does Mai look good in it?\"","Forbidden Land Exclusive\n\"Pr-prey? No problem, I\'m ready. Master, please... Eh? You are the prey?! That\'s quite the surprise... In that case, please don\'t be afraid, I am... I\'m coming now.\"","Savoring the Warmth Exclusive\n\"Hyah! W-who\'s there? ...Master? I didn\'t know you were here too, how disrespectful of me, being seen like this... I heard the hot springs here have the power to purify one\'s body and mind, do you want to try? Maybe, this will also increase your luck on the mahjong table...\"","Sanrio characters X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"\'Oh my, I fell down. Now I can\'t get up unless someone picks me up!\' …When the heroine said something like this in the novel I read, a reliable person would appear. And since you came, I think this line is the real deal.\"","Snowkissed Tidings Exclusive\n\"Happy New Year, Master. I tried a new recipe... Please, have the first bite. H-how is it? Is it to your liking? Phew... That\'s a relief. I was worried I\'d mess up my first try, but I\'m glad it turned out well. Can we do this every New Year\'s Eve? I... I really want to keep cooking for you.\"","Nadeshiko’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Nadeshiko\n\"Pick one: go for a ride or have a one-on-one Mahjong match with me?\"","Beach Party Exclusive\n\"Sunlight, ocean waves and good wine are a great combination, don\'t you think so?\"","\"What? Surprised to see me in kimono? Or do you think this look doesn\'t suit me? Hehe~ Relax, it\'s New Year\'s, however eager you are about going for a drive with me, don\'t forget to pay respects to the gods at Mahjong Soul Shrine before we go out~\"","Quadrupath Adventurer Exclusive\n\"Hurry up my crew! Speed is key if we wanna get back in time for the party at the inn, so it\'s all up to how fast you do the job!\"","Cozy Playtime Exclusive\n\"The other game controller is over there and sit wherever you like. Let me see how far we are from reaching 100% achievements... Wow, there are still lots of missions we need to do, let\'s dive in! Hey, darling, don\'t be nervous, if you have trouble I\'ll help you. How about we get some drinks to relax?\"","Yui Yagi’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Yui Yagi\n\"Senpai, would you like to take a sit on the swing?\"","Christmas Carnival Exclusive\n\"You have been staring at my legs. I knew you had a thing for girls\' feet. \"","Halloween Party Exclusive\n\"Go, butterflies--Bring that person to me.\"","Moonlight Waltz Exclusive\n\"Senpai, how about a dance? I learnt some simple dance steps before coming here, but the chance of me stepping on your foot is still 32.7%. I hope you won\'t mind.\"","Heartfelt Summer Exclusive\n\"\'Butterflies are attracted by beautiful flowers,\' yes, that\'s right, but why do you bring this up now, senpai?\"","Quadrupath Adventurer Exclusive\n\"I don\'t get it... If magic requires long chants, won\'t the caster get attacked during that time? It\'s illogical.\"","Sanrio characters X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"What\'s the matter, senpai? You\'re staring at me... Hmm, do you want to play with the little one? Then, go ahead.\"","Shape of a Fading Echo Exclusive\n\"Senpai... come up and see. The lanterns on the lake are beautiful. I\'ve mastered lightness arts, so you\'ll be safe. Just... hold me close.\"","Riu Kujou’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Riu Kujou\n\"Would you like some tea?  I can remember your flavor. \"","Beach Party Exclusive\n\"I won\'t show you any mercy even if you praise my looks.\"","Snowy New Year Exclusive\n\"And one more stroke! Try harder, or your face will be covered by ink. Well, if you beg for mercy, I might consider going easy on you.\"","Soul-Colored Fantasy Exclusive\n\"The princess\'s command guides my fists! I am sure you have engraved her highness\'s name in your heart. Now, let\'s pledge our loyalty together: We will dedicate our lives to the service of her highness!\"","Heartbeat Velocity\n\"Oh! Victory on the first battle? Not bad at all. Are you tired? Lean here and rest a bit, I\'ll take care of the car maintenance afterward. ...You want to take a photo of me? Hah, seems like you\'re not that tired, huh? Hurry up and pack up the protective gear for me!\"","Freshman Mornings Exclusive\n\"Shhh, this is study hall – we have to be quiet. Whatever you have to say can wait until after class! N-Not even if it\'s a confession of lo... No, absolutely not! ...Honestly! Something that important should be said in a more private, serious setting, you know?\"","Xenia’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Xenia\n\"You promised that one day we would travel together. \"","Halloween Party Exclusive\n\"This costume mimics a creature known as a succubus in my country. They are very skillful at seduction...\"","Beach Party Exclusive\n\"No matter what country it is, everyone loves the sea just the same. Well, I think you will also love my sandwiches and tea!\"","Spring Song Exclusive\n\"What do you think? To blend in the festive mood, I purposely chose this traditional outfit, how do I look? In the shop I bought it the clerk said the golden pattern is not printed, but embroidered with traditional technique, isn\'t it astonishing? How about we visit the artisans sometime to see how it\'s done?\"","Sanrio characters X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"Keeping up with the formalities for a long time can be tiring. One needs to take a break every once in a while. I hereby declare that today I will spend my time as I please.\"","Freshman Mornings Exclusive\n\"Surprised to see me in a school uniform? ...Well, it\'s your fault. You go on and on about Asaha High School, so I had to come see for myself if this place actually lives up to all your praise.\"","Kaavi’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Kaavi\n\"I’ll make an exception to give you a fortune telling.\"","Summer of Destiny Exclusive\n\"Sunshine, beach, alcohol… Hmm, it’s quite a nice seaside trip worthy of anticipation. So, what activities have you prepared for?\"","Daybreak in G Major Exclusive\n\"There\'s still time before the prophesied bells shall ring. With nothing else to do, how about you take advantage of this splendid ball and give me another dance?\"","Natsuki Shinomiya’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Natsuki Shinomiya\n\"Shh... You should call me White Night now. \"","Halloween Party Exclusive\n\"Haha, the dark red threads under the skin are so breathtaking. Tonight, you belong to me.\"","\"If this is a showdown, shouldn\'t we give it a stake? For example, if I win, you will be the assistant of \"White Night\" this year. And if you win, you can make a slightly demanding request, how about that?\"","Heartfelt Summer Exclusive\n\"A seagull is rummaging through my bag? How come, there\'re no chips or the like in it... Can\'t believe it\'s actually happening?! Hey! Stop that!\"","Wanjirou’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Wanjirou\n\" I was one of the ex-Mahjong players of Mahjong Soul Temple. \"","Halloween Party Exclusive\n\"Sush… keep silent. Tonight, I am nothing but a quiet scarecrow.\"","Beachside Vacation Exclusive\n\"It\'s time to show true artistry! Eating ramen while surfing, play and eat at the same time, woof!\"","Book of Winter Dreams Exclusive\n\"Now that Santa Claus has upgraded to me, my reindeer should be upgraded to a motorcycle! Not only does it look cooler, it increases gift delivery efficiency twentyfold!\"","Sora Ichinose’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Sora Ichinose\n\" I have many more things that I want to share with you.  \"","Christmas Carnival Exclusive\n\"This is my first Christmas with you... Can we celebrate it again in the future together?\"","Spring Homecoming Exclusive\n\"Long time no see? Didn\'t we see each other all the time during the vacation... But it indeed has been a while since the last time we read together in school. I just bought this picture book. Wan-Wanna read it together?\"","Spring Song Exclusive\n\"From a scientific viewpoint, it\'s still far from real spring. But people like to consider the Spring Festival a signal that spring is coming, and it\'s palpable that everyone is getting energetic. I also seem to see you more, which makes me happy.\"","Bond of the Restless Night Exclusive\n\"Here. Apply this potion and all the scary stuff will steer clear of you. {name}, you\'ll have a peaceful night... What? Mosquitos? Hold on a second, I\'ll whip up something for that right away...\"","Hideki Akechi’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Hideki Akechi\n\"Could you sit here for a while? Just stay with me for a moment. \"","Halloween Party Exclusive\n\"Good evening, Hideki Akechi, the messenger with dark wings, has come to greet you to that moonlit country with me.\"","Summer of Destiny Exclusive\n\"The sea breeze here is rather gentle, come sit down and have a rest. At this pace, our little castle will be finished before the sun sets, and I’m sure you will like it!\"","Seize the Date Exclusive\n\"{name}? I am surprised to run into you here. As you can see, I came here with my family, but... we got separated and I\'m on my own now. If you\'re alone too, how about we stick with each other and go watch the fireworks together?\"","Balmy Haze Exclusive\n\"Did I just... fall asleep? There haven\'t been many club activities or anything stressful going on lately. The reason for this might just be because having you around makes me feel especially relaxed.\"","Keikumusume’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Keikumusume\n\"Do you also like to read light novels?\"","Limited Outfit from Summer Festival - Beach Party event\n\"Apart from staying at home reading novels, I do occasionally go out!\"","Sara’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Sara\nThe dancer comes along with the scent of rosemary.","New Year\'s First Visit Exclusive\n\"Here\'s a dance that I learned specifically for the New Year.\"","Spring Homecoming Exclusive\n\"Senpai, wanna go to the school with me today? Haha, just kidding. I tried my school uniform on a whim, and it looked surprisingly good. Should I wear it on the stage next time?\"","Heartfelt Summer Exclusive\n\"Oh my, is this sunscreen for me? A lot of people would assume I don\'t need it just because of my appearance. Thank you, and... Can I ask for another favor? There\'re always some places my hands can\'t reach, hehe...\"","Quadrupath Adventurer Exclusive\n\"Cornered? Well, are you sure you are safe if you can only see the enemy in front of you?\"","Echoes of Rejoicing Exclusive\n\"What a pleasure to see you on the first day of the New Year. Even though \'Soul\' isn\'t performing today, I will still offer you a special treat – would you like to try this delectable GRAPE?\"","Hana Ninomiya’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Hana Ninomiya\n\"It\'s my first time wearing something like this. How do I look? \"","Spring Celebration Exclusive\n\"Here you are, I just finished this calligraphy. I wish you a prosperous and healthy year of Gengzi (2020). \"","Summer of Destiny Exclusive\n\"Although I prefer the greenhouse of the gardening club to outdoors, I still want to thank you for coming to the beach with me today. I have had a great time... Indeed, I am very glad to see a new side of you.\"","Roomful of Aroma Exclusive\n\"Even the cats in the café are more active during the opening hours than usual, so I can\'t lose to them. Though it\'s my first time working part-time at a café, I will endeavor to be the best maid.\"","Book of Winter Dreams Exclusive\n\"Even with this new dress, I don\'t feel any more noticeable... Eh? R-really? It looks good? Thank you. Once again, you\'re the first one to notice me.\"","Nana Shiraishi’s default look","An outfit acquired when your bond with Nana Shiraishi reaches maximum","Beach Party Exclusive\n\"Soon, I\'ll be able to swim here as much as I want. Just this thought alone makes me full of energy to start cleaning.\"","Roomful of Aroma Exclusive\n\"Cleaning the café is one of the responsibilities of the maids, not to mention, junior is our customer now, so let me do the deed. Cherish this moment, for this is a rare chance where you get my service!\"","Book of Winter Dreams Exclusive\n\"Exercising with a beautiful senpai in her festival-exclusive outfit on Christmas morning—this is what youth is all about, Junior!\"","Hinata Takanashi’s default look","An outfit acquired when your bond with Hinata Takanashi reaches maximum","Sweet Refreshment Exclusive\n\"Welcome! Can I interest you in some dessert today, or a limited-edition Big Three Dragons omurice? Or… The buy-one-get-one-50%-off coffee is also a good choice, hehe!\"","Firework Date Exclusive\n\"What do you want to have first, marshmallow or takoyaki? Oh, there\'s taiyaki over there... {name}, quick, you can scoop goldfish at this stand! Wow! Do we have enough time to try out every stand tonight?\"","Soul-Colored Fantasy Exclusive\n\"I command you in the name of Fruit Doughnuts, listen to my summon and show yourself, my messenger— Eh? Is my summoning circle faulty? I wanted to summon the swordmaster, but now... even the attribute doesn\'t look right... May I ask, are you... here for the Mahjong Soul War?\"","Cozy Playtime Exclusive\n\"An afternoon all alone with you, and even the sunshine is so mellow... Haaah... Oh no, I\'m getting sleepy, but that\'d be a waste of precious time with {name}... How about we try our hand at making some bonsai ice cream together?\"","Oracle\'s Legacy Exclusive\n\"They say that if you make a wish when a swing is at its very highest, it reaches the ears of the gods much faster! Ah, b-but... if my wish was, say, to spend more time with you, {name} would probably help make that one come true yourself, wouldn\'t you? Hehe...\"","Haruna Igarashi’s default look","\"Ta-da! Haruna\'s stray-cat-cafe is now open. Dear customer, would you like an ice pop?\"","Beach Party Exclusive\n\"Alright, here\'s the deal! If Haruna wins the water-gun fight, you will treat Haruna to 10 ice pops today!\"","Spring Homecoming Exclusive\n\"Haruna drew this cat. Isn\'t it majestic? With the painting brush mom gave me, I can draw cats of all kinds of colors. Haruna\'s cat legion will rise again!\"","Fortuitous Beginning Exclusive\n\"Kitty Warriors, charge! The first one who manages to stick this \'Great Blessing\' talisman on {name}\'s forehead gets an ice lolly from me!\"","Cozy Playtime Exclusive\n\"Argh... Vanilla, blueberry, chocolate, there are so many different flavors for popsicles... Popsicles are like balloons, flying up high, and taking Haruna to the kitty park... They are so warm and soft, just like {name}\'s hand, amazing... Eh, wait! When did {name} arrive? Wahhhhh—\"","Anju Suzumiya’s default look","\"Question: Why is KR-976 appearing more often in the life report of {name}?\"","\"After testing, we found out that the battery of KR-976 can still last for around 2 hours and 30 minutes. If {name} is sleepy, KR-976 may provide you with an exclusive rechargeable sofa. Rest assured, KR-976 will be looking after you during your rest.\"","Firework Date Exclusive\n\"Question: {name} is in a good mood because of the food, the environment or the pretty fireworks? KR-976 can sense {name}\'s mood, but cannot trace the source. KR-976 would like to be granted access to this information in order to bring happiness to {name} in the future.\"","Day of Celebration Exclusive\n\"Question: When should KR-976 hand {name} the red packets? Now, or after the fireworks show in the evening? ...You ask why I give you red packets? Em... Answer: I received them from my elders this morning when we went to greet everyone, and I thought I should share these fortuitous gifts with you.\"","Pointe Monologue Exclusive\n\"Analysis: Today, {name}\'s frequency of looking at KR-976 was double the daily average. Conclusion: {name} has a preference for the white ballet dress. Updating preference list. Data backed up to KR-976\'s top secret archive.\"","Joseph’s default look","\"Yo, partner! I\'ve found a new destination for us. Let\'s go!\"","Snowy New Year Exclusive\n\"Happy New Year! My friend. Never have I expected that one would like a gentleman in traditional Japanese clothes.\"","Osamu Saitou’s default look","\"Like I said, you just have to be yourself in front of me. I like just the way you are.\"","Firework Date Exclusive\n\"Instead of watching fireworks, I\'d rather spend my time reading more reports, or even playing Mahjong for a bit, but... It seems I\'m unable to refuse your invitation.\"","Winter Warmth Exclusive\n\"You are not late, I\'m early. Hmm... I think it\'s because I look forward to today\'s schedule.\"","Sawako Kitami’s default look","\"Summer\'s coming soon! I\'m really looking forward to it, because it\'s the first summer we will spend together since I met you!\"","Snowy Night Whisper Exclusive\n\"While preparing Christmas gifts for the kids, I\'ve also prepared yours! Take a seat here. I can\'t wait to see you unbox it.\"","Moonlight Waltz Exclusive\n\"Hush, just enjoy a night like this. What a housewife does best is time management, and then one only needs to do the right thing at the right time. Like now, let\'s appreciate the joy of the dance party!\"","Pillow Whispers Exclusive\n\"After a day of hard work, it\'s only now that I get time for myself... Ah, I\'m not complaining, it\'s just... Look at that sleeping face, how do I say it, I feel really content.\"","Heartbeat Velocity\n\"Ah... the feeling of being watched by you is quite nice. But please, {name}, just like you care about me, pay more attention to the steering wheel in front of you, okay? Hehe... After all, veering off the track during a race is very dangerous, just like it\'s easy to stray off course in life...\"","Balmy Haze Exclusive\n\"Oh, did I lose track of time again? You didn\'t notice either, {name}? The water\'s just the right temperature, and with no interruptions... I guess we both got a little too caught up. You know, {name}, it\'s perfectly fine to let go of the little things now and then and just indulge a bit, don\'t you think?\"","Ein’s default look","\"Hold on to my tail. Make sure you follow me! I\'ll be in great trouble if I lose you while hunting. But don\'t worry, even if you do get lost, I can always find you. Haha!\"","Summer of Destiny Exclusive\n\"While I usually hunt in the jungle, but actually surfing in the ocean is also my specialty. Well? Would you like to join me in feeling the passion of the waves? Haha~\"","Close Your Eyes Exclusive\n\"Aha! Isn\'t Halloween great, with how a prey would actually dare appear before me so willingly, are you lost or what? With how cute you are, how about I allow you to get a head start... Hmm, maybe 39 meters?\"","Snowkissed Tidings Exclusive\n\"What beautiful snow. A good omen for the year. I heard the lines for prayers are endless at the shrine today. But I\'m not joining that crowd. After all... my target for the day is already right in front of me. Hahaha... Kidding, kidding. But if you\'re feeling chilly, why not come closer? Here\'s a secret: A fox\'s arms are the warmest trap you\'ll find in winter. Once you\'re in my sights... you can\'t run away.\"","Momo Hina’s default look","\"Wow, what to do, I\'m late for the tea party! Mr. Rabbit, what should I do?\"","Wonderful Youth Exclusive\n\"Why does Momo like Mr.Rabbit? Eh? Isn\'t this just as natural as how flowers bloom when spring comes?\"","Summertime Coffeeshop Exclusive\n\"You are punctual today as well! The White Queen\'s tea party is about to start and this is the first time I\'m in charge of the preparations! I\'ll do my best for Mr. Rabbit so I hope you\'ll have fun today!\"","Book of Winter Dreams Exclusive\n\"Is it snowing in the fairyland too? How I wish to see it with Mr. Rabbit.\"","Summer Night Breeze Exclusive\n\"Woaaah! Momo just turned into a little mermaid in the lemonade! This pool party is, like, a special Wonderland theme, right? Hanging out with Mr. Rabbit, my luck is gonna be totally, totally maxed out!\"","Zan Tsukimi’s default look","\"Although today is just a regular day like any other, shall we make it our secret anniversary?\"","Spring Homecoming Exclusive\n\"It\'s your turn. Take off your shoes and get on the scale... Well, inconvenient as it is, it\'s necessary to take the regular physical examination. Don\'t worry, I won\'t tell anyone about your height or weight.\"","Forbidden Land Exclusive\n\"This is the first time I\'ve been driven to show this form... How embarrassing. However, sworn on my pride as a werewolf, before my blade and bones are all broken, no one shall pass!\"","Savoring the Warmth Exclusive\n\"Training the body is the same as training the mind. Especially when you have lost too many times in mahjong and feel dispirited, taking a rest is very important, haha. Anyways, coming to this place far from the city to relax with you is a real pleasure, surely this can help revive your spirit too.\"","Kirara Fujimoto’s default look","\"Look at me! Cheers—yeah! This photo marks our first date!\"","Snowy New Year Exclusive\n\"Ta-da! Hot and fresh New Year Kirara. As you can see, traditional clothes can also be stylish on Kirara!\"","Perfect Holiday Exclusive\n\"Wanna play a game of Mahjong? What? I said it already half an hour ago, no need to sleep so early. For youngsters like us, doesn\'t nightlife mean spending the whole night browsing on the phone after saying goodnight? Well, in my eyes, Mahjong is far more interesting than the phone, don\'t you agree?\"","Savoring the Warmth Exclusive\n\"Don\'t just stand there, come on! Nothing\'s better than taking a soak after an exhausting day! I asked you to accompany me for a whole day of shopping, so of course I will prepare some appropriate rewards. Thoughtful of me, right?\"","Freshman Mornings Exclusive\n\"You\'re so slow! What took you so long? I\'ve already had time to redo my makeup! To compensate for all that wasted time, I\'m just gonna have to ride faster now. So hurry up, get on, and wrap your arms around my waist. Got it?!\"","Kaguyahime’s default look","\"Countless people want to serve me, but you are my favorite. From now on, you are my general for conquering the world!\"","Snowy Night Whisper Exclusive\n\"Tired already, mortal? Catch up! Hehe! Tonight I\'m going to \'surprise\' those who are expecting their Christmas gifts!\"","Festive Aroma Exclusive\n\"Ever heard the saying \'hiding a beauty in a golden palace\'? Well, do you have any new wishes you want me to fulfill this year? For example, building a gorgeous palace made from precious wood and decorated with rare gems, and then worshiping me inside it to monopolize my blessing, uhehe? I would let you try~\"","Dripping Glamour Exclusive\n\"O rude human, how dare you trespass my private hot spring! ...Of course this place is private, all the hot springs in the vicinity have been taken over by me! But considering that you\'ve been devout to me day in and day out, I could let you share this place. But you are only allowed to use the smallest pool, you hear?\"","Draped Murmurs Exclusive\n\"Etiquette for attending balls? How foolish! Such mundane constraints are meaningless to a deity like me! But you... hehe, for the rest of tonight, you shall stay by my side. Devote yourself to serving your adorable deity – that\'s the only thing you need to worry about!\"","Idle Hours Exclusive\n\"I\'m over here, silly. And you\'re just standing there with that blank look on your face... which I\'ve gotten all on camera! Making a deity personally come and get you for a date... a mortal like you is just begging for punishment. So, offer up your devotion, give me a little leg massage, and take lots of cute pictures of me. Then I\'ll think about letting you off the hook this time, hehehe.\"","Ren Kisaragi’s default look","\"Hmm? Since when did you like to watch others get changed? Do you want to appear on my \'trouble students\' list so much?\"","Code of Shadows Exclusive\n\"Entry prohibited, you can still turn back... Or do you want me to take hold of you personally?\"","Brilliant New Year Exclusive\n\"The onsen hotel we are visiting today is owned by a friend of my father\'s, his udon is really delicious. Near the hotel is a shopping street and you can get a lot of food rarely seen in One Han City... What? Em, ahem, isn\'t making a detailed travel plan before coming on a trip with you the most natural thing in the world?","Usumi Ishihara’s default look","\"As my member, are you really only going to eat? If you don\'t come and help, I will take away your desserts for the week with no m-e-r-c-y!\"","\"Common Christmas activities would probably be looking at snowflakes, counting the stars and waiting for Santa? But I would like to take you to eat the Yule log cake at C\'est, the brownie at The Monsoon, the Black Forest gateau at Éternité... Hmm, the reason? Sharing happiness with those you love is the best embodiment of the Chrismas spirit~\"","Beachside Vacation Exclusive\n\"Yaahoooo! There are only two good things about summer, shaved ice and the sea... Wait, now there are three, with you being the third. Hmm, vanilla ice cream with chocolate sauce and cookie crisps might be even better, how about we try some new ways to have fun? For example, let me throw you into the water, then I jump after you, and we can get shaved ice after we get out!\"","Eliisa’s default look","\"Hey! Mr. Wolf, look! The ranch had a bumper harvest this year. Grandma sent these from the ranch and asked me to give them to you, hehe!\"","\"Liisa Liisa has done reading the entire fairytale. Why is Mr.Wolf still awake?Perhaps Liisa Liisa can count sheep for you, one sheep, two sheep, three sheep... Snore... Snore...\"","Festive Aroma Exclusive\n\"Mr. Wolf, Mr. Wolf, the vice president said I\'m \'like a sheep entering a tiger\'s mouth,\' what does it mean? When Liisa Liisa visits Mr. Wolf with Shaun, shouldn\'t it be \'like a sheep entering a wolf\'s mouth?\' ...Anyways, if you are hungry, instead of eating Liisa Liisa or Shaun, eat this squirrel fish Liisa Liisa brought. I heard in the city that one should eat fish on this special day to be blessed with good fortune for the whole year!\"","Close Your Eyes Exclusive\n\"Grrr—! It\'s a landslide victory for Liisa Liisa... Eh? Ehhhh! Mr. Wolf, save me, I\'m gonna fall! Em... This model chainsaw is real heavy, and it is hard to make a cool pose with it. So then, it\'s decided, starting from tomorrow, Liisa Liisa shall exercise alongside Mr. Wolf, hehe.\"","Heartbeat Velocity Exclusive\n\"Wow— Car racing is so awesome, the atmosphere is just like at the ranch... Eh? What kind of atmosphere? Mmm, it\'s the kind where you can face the wind and move forward freely, hehe. Mr. Wolf, how about another round with Liisa Liisa?\"","Song of the Bells Exclusive\n\"Hehe, the snow\'s so fluffy today! It\'s like stepping on wool back at the ranch! Mr. Wolf, wanna build snowmen with me? Liisa Liisa will make the cute snow-sheep, and you make the cool... good wolf who always protects me! Shaun can be our supervisor! Hehe, with Liisa Liisa, Mr. Wolf, and Shaun together, today\'s a big win – we\'re making the happiest Christmas ranch in the world!\"","Chihori Terasaki’s default look","\"I\'m wondering if this leisurely afternoon you\'ve brought here is a good thing or a bad thing for me... It looks like I\'m getting \'lazy\' too, haha!\"","Seize the Date Exclusive\n\"Hurry up, or I\'ll leave you behind~ I know this is a rare opportunity for us to spend time together and that I shouldn\'t put work before you, but it\'s a super big scoop this time! I promise, when this is done, you get to decide how we\'ll spend the rest of the time, how\'s that?\"","Playful Summertime Exclusive\n\"Come sit over here, let\'s have a drink together and enjoy a sunbath. Heehee, do you need me to apply some sunscreen for you? Make sure to pay attention to my technique, because I\'ll be conducting an exclusive interview about your experience later.\"","Saki Miyanaga’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Saki Miyanaga","Saki: The Nationals x Mahjong Soul Limited-time Collab\nThe unattainable orange flower in bright bloom, subtle but powerful.","Saki: The Nationals X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"I feel restless... Should\'ve brought a book with me.\"","Nodoka Haramura’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Nodoka Haramura","Saki: The Nationals x Mahjong Soul Limited-time Collab\nEnjoy, the sweet scent that is embalmed in the heart.","Saki: The Nationals X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"Put Etopen on my thigh... Like this?\"","Koromo Amae’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Koromo Amae","Saki: The Nationals x Mahjong Soul Limited-time Collab\nThe innocence and enthusiasm bursting out between red and white!","Saki: The Nationals X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"Where\'s everyone else? Don\'t tell me only Koromo is dressed like this...\"","Teru Miyanaga’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Teru Miyanaga","Saki: The Nationals x Mahjong Soul Limited-time Collab\nDeep and noble eyes, like the stars in the night sky.","Saki: The Nationals X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"Is the photo shoot not over yet... No, I have nothing against photos, it\'s just the ice cream is melting.\"","Fu Ji’s default look","\"You look luckier recently. It\'s definitely because you have been visiting my dojo. Good kid! Remember to keep doing it, haha!\"","Spring Relaxation Exclusive\n\"I never thought there could exist a place on par with Luck and Fortune... Hoho, how nice of you to choose such a fancy hot spring to receive me, good job~ Now, I don\'t want to take advantage of your generosity, so I\'ll award you something in return: this whole year, you\'ll get 20% off of your entry fee at Luck and Fortune~\"","Sugary Magic Exclusive\n\"You want to ask me how this floating box effect came to be? If I say I used my divine power, would you believe me? Hehe, of course that\'s not it, these boxes are empty~ Rest assured, my present for you won\'t leave you empty-handed~\"","Beachside Vacation Exclusive\n\"Considering the fact that you invited me here with sincerity, I won\'t hold the hot weather against you. Your face is getting a sunburn, get in the water with me to cool down.\"","Sanrio characters X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"You say you saw the cute kitty girl on the fan popping off into the real world? Shh— Others might hear you! Come closer! You can\'t tell anyone else what I\'m about to show you, OK? ...Now, only our VVVVIPs are allowed to meet her! Well, isn\'t she super adorable?\"","Joy Woven In Exclusive\n\"Perfect timing! I just finished painting these goldfish, and the ink has settled nicely. So we\'re down to the final step: painting the eyes. You know what they say – once the eyes are painted, they come alive! They\'ll swim right off the paper and bring good fortune straight to you. Come on, this is my special spring ritual, and I need you to complete it with me!\"","Qi Xi’s default look","\"I\'ve spent all my time on that old woman\'s mission. It won\'t hurt if I occasionally take a break. Look, aren\'t my red strings stunning? Hehe, I don\'t mind giving you one.\"","Heartfelt Summer Exclusive\n\"Tch... What a fool, this is no ordinary sandcastle, it\'s a masterpiece that took me several hours to complete. No more talk, I have to be on guard against vandals. If you have time, come help me.\"","Quadrupath Adventurer Exclusive\n\"An archer that lacks close-quarter combat skills is incompetent... Where did you hear such nonsense? With my archery skills, do you honestly think anyone can come near me? What a joke.\"","Song of the Bells Exclusive\n\"Don\'t get the wrong idea! I just happen to be working here, okay? I wasn\'t waiting for you or anything... But, uh, since you showed up, just stick around. There\'s gonna be fireworks in the square when the bells ring later. A-and I still need a Christmas Eve case study for my \'Research on Human Dating Habits.\' So, you know...\"","Yumeko Jabami’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Yumeko Jabami","Mahjong Soul X Kakegurui xx Collab\nWelcome to the Floral Dance Special Show! Please have a nice time!","Mary Saotome’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Mary Saotome","Mahjong Soul X Kakegurui xx Collab\nThe moment this outfit stole your attention, defeat is almost inevitable.","Midari Ikishima’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Midari Ikishima","Mahjong Soul X Kakegurui xx Collab\nDon\'t you want some octopus balls made by the Beautification Council President using the \"special sauce recipe\"? Just open your mouth!","Kirari Momobami’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Kirari Momobami","Mahjong Soul X Kakegurui xx Collab\nThe mortals can only kneel before the secret abyss in Hyakkaou Private Academy.","Reina Nanami’s default look","\"Where to stroll next? I wish to visit every road {name} has been to. Is that alright?\"","\"Santa has been busy this year as well, so Reina will reimburse the gift he forgot to give you~ Here, steaming hot black chocolate mocha, with your preferred sweetness. Would it entice you to show your smile tonight?\"","Pillow Whispers Exclusive\n\"S-Sorry, I somehow fell asleep as we chatted... Did I look weird in sleep?\"","Spring Blooms at the Window Exclusive\n\"I\'ve prepared some origami cranes. It\'s said that writing your first wish inside the crane makes it more likely to come true. {name}, do you have any wishes? For me, I hope to see more of the world by your side in this new year.\"","A-37’s default look","\"Don\'t worry. I\'ll find you wherever you are.\"","Firework Date Exclusive\n\"Fireworks? I don\'t know... I shouldn\'t look away from my employer. If I have to say... You can take that as you being more beautiful than the firework.\"","Summertime Coffeeshop Exclusive\n\"Instead of visiting me, you are actually here to pet the cats, right? Don\'t worry, being enamored by fluffy animals is not a sin... Don\'t look at me like I\'m a cat, face the reality, I\'m not a cat and bribing me with cat food is futile... Coffee won\'t work either.\"","Bond of the Restless Night Exclusive\n\"Bring light to this one trapped in darkness... My answer is clear--no need. I don\'t need the light even if it comes from you. If you don\'t want to be pulled into an even deeper mire of night by me, you\'d better leave now while you still can...\"","Hibiki Himekawa’s default look","\"You are still as stubborn as ever. Spill the tea. What\'s the challenge you\'re up to today? I am invincible. And I\'ll make sure you understand that this time!\"","Fortuitous Beginning Exclusive\n\"Now, Hibiki fans, are you ready? Hibiki\'s Extraordinary New Year Livestream is about to start, let\'s count down together, 3, 2, 1! Happy New Year!\"","Encountering Starlight Exclusive\n\"Hehe, welcome to the first live of the world\'s greatest lead singer! ...Hey, you, the third one in the front row, are you getting distracted? As punishment, buy 10 sets of Hibiki\'s merch after the live!\"","Ryan’s default look","\"I\'m not sleepy... My eyes are just a bit itchy. I can still play with you, , really! So please don\'t leave me to sleep alone, please?\"","Sugary Magic Exclusive\n\"Shhh— Now is Ryan\'s magic time! Put your hand on the box and think of what you like... Mhm, I\'ve heard your heart, open it up... Ta-da, it\'s me! Sure enough, I am onesan\'s favorite!\"","Close Your Eyes Exclusive\n\"Onee-sama, do you know that the redder the Halloween apple is, the higher the probability it is poisoned? But if it\'s a gift from you, I\'ll of course eat it all. Just... don\'t forget to wake me up afterwards, onee-sama. Heehee, I wonder what approach you will take.\"","Ayako Morikawa’s default look","\"Is this the kind of sunshine {name} likes? If staying longer under the sun means I can also make many friends like {name}, I...I\'ll do my best. Why don\'t we enjoy the sunshine together tomorrow?\"","Perfect Holiday Exclusive\n\"Ah... This is not a summoning circle, but a dream-catching circle... It\'s my first sleepover, so I have no idea how to entertain a guest. I think... if you have a good dream tonight then you\'ll have a nice time here...\"","Daybreak in G Major Exclusive\n\"A dan-dance with you? ...I do want to, but dancing would require me to put my hands on you, right? I\'m afraid I\'d bring you misfortune by doing so... I really wish you\'d be the luckiest person in the world.\"","Bond of the Restless Night Exclusive\n\"Phew, how wonderful... It\'s you, {name}. Now I can finally breathe easy and be your bride... Oh, I-I mean, I\'m in character today. The role of... a ghost bride. Umm, if you don\'t mind, m-may I start my lines? Well, here goes... Hehe, since you\'ve come all this way, w-why not stay and become the other half of my soul?\"","Song of the Bells Exclusive\n\"It started snowing... You\'ve got snowflakes in your hair... Your hands must be freezing, too... I\'m so sorry I asked you to meet me out here... A-actually, Hanako told me the other day that... um... if you wear antlers on Christmas to see someone you care about... the Reindeer Spirit will bless them... So that\'s why I did it... I... I\'m being too selfish, aren\'t I...?\"","Natsuhiko Takikawa’s default look","\"Speaking of which, while there were so many people cheering on the pitch, I only heard your voice, so I had to make it a goal, haha!\"","Dripping Glamour Exclusive\n\"It\'s quite hot near the hot water\'s outlet, so if you step into the pool from there you might get scalded. You should go to where the water is shallow to get used to the temperature first and then come over... Hmm, after a day of matches, a nice soak in the hot spring is the best way to relax!\"","Day of Celebration Exclusive\n\"Lantern riddles?! That\'s not for me, I\'m really not good with those since you either know the answer or not... Oh, if it\'s the 1st prize at the temple fair that you are aiming for, we can win that in the lion dance competition too. I\'m very good at physical challenges, just you see!\"","Idle Hours Exclusive\n\"Whoa, {name}! Check it out! I totally learned how to skateboard! It\'s actually way easier than I thought! You wanna give it a shot? Oh, but hey, no worries if you\'re not into it. We\'ve got all day, so whatever you wanna do, I\'m down!\"","Shigeru Akagi’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Shigeru Akagi","AKAGI Collab Limited\nThe unparalleled Mahjong genius, the dragon of light.","Iwao Washizu’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Iwao Washizu","AKAGI Collab Limited\nThe undisputed ruler of three worlds, the emperor of darkness.","Kazuha Saionji’s default look","\"My father once taught me that the sword should follow the guidance of the heart. The sword of a swordsman should only be drawn for justice and ideals, and a swordsman\'s heart should be filled with light and goodness. Your goodness has been the light that dispersed the mist in my heart. From now on, I will never waver again in my pursuit of swordsmanship.\"","Nanaha Onodera’s default look","\"The truth in here does not equal the reality anywhere else. Welcome to the world of love and desire I\'ve poured my heart and soul into. Now, tell me your thoughts after reading it.\"","Traditions of Summer Exclusive\n\"Oh... Fancy meeting you at this desolate place, maybe it could be said that \'our hearts are in harmony.\' Well, as a reward, take a piece of this snack.\"","Summer Night Breeze Exclusive\n\"I came here hoping the sound of the waves would give me some inspiration for my writing... but it\'s hard to ignore your gaze, you know? It\'s okay, though. The evening breeze has arrived. How about we listen to the story it\'s telling for a little while?\"","Sammir’s default look","\"Is there any song you want to hear, or how about the one that just came to my mind? This melody sprang to my mind just now when I saw you walking toward me. I\'m sure it will be a romantic piece.\"","Spring Relaxation Exclusive\n\"I thought this is a private onsen, you\'re at the wrong place... Hmm, my bad, I must have forgotten the time schedule. How about I buy you some night snacks as an apology? I\'ve heard the takoyaki of this place is very famous, with 26 different flavors available. I think... you\'ll like it.\"","Ode to Grace Exclusive\n\"Ho? So many birds... Little birdies, are you here to cheer for me? With your help, I hope my charming guest will like the next song even more. {name}, did you know that no performance before, no matter how grandiose the occasion was, made me as nervous as I am now? Well, are you ready to listen to the music of my heart?\"","Oracle\'s Legacy Exclusive\n\"You\'re having a restless night, aren\'t you? Would you like me to tell you a bedtime story? Perhaps one about the stars and their signs? ...No, it\'s no bother at all, really. I\'d quite enjoy it. Shall we begin with {name}\'s star sign, then? It all started many, many years ago...\"","Kaguya Shinomiya’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Kaguya Shinomiya","Mahjong Soul X Kaguya-sama: Love Is War Collab\nAre you trying to guess my escape route? How cute...","Miyuki Shirogane’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Miyuki Shirogane","Mahjong Soul X Kaguya-sama: Love Is War Collab\nI kindly accept the master painting \"Kaguya Shinomiya\'s Smile.\" – Phantom Thief S","Ai Hayasaka’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Ai Hayasaka","Mahjong Soul X Kaguya-sama: Love Is War Collab\nA rope ladder that goes high into the clouds is a unique charm of being a phantom thief.","Kei Shirogane’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Kei Shirogane","Mahjong Soul X Kaguya-sama: Love Is War Collab\nThe Blue Rose will take your most precious treasure tonight, be prepared!","Yuzu’s default look","\"Wow, I didn\'t imagine you would be able to find this place. In this case, let\'s say you past the witch\'s trial, and this is your reward: \'How to Become a Witch in 100 Days - Beginner\'s Level\'. Well? Are you unsatisfied with this brilliant training manual I wrote myself? If not, then start practicing today, the Red Panda Squad will keep an eye on you!“","Pillow Whispers Exclusive\n\"Shhh... Be quiet, it took me lots of effort to get the Red Panda Squad to sleep.\"","Brilliant New Year Exclusive\n\"Oh no! It\'s falling over... Save me, {name}, please! Ahaha, I didn\'t imagine that you would show your power of justice on the first day of the year, saving me and our dinner tonight. Looks like in the new year, I must work hard to prove myself as the witch of justice to you!\"","Playful Summertime Exclusive\n\"Argh, how is it? Even without using magic, you are still inferior to Yuzu in a water gun fight! ...Wait, Yuzu hasn\'t said start yet, you\'re cheating! You who scorn justice, prepare to face the punishment!\"","Pointe Monologue Exclusive\n\"Argh, {name}, you\'re so slow! You almost missed my performance! ...It\'s not like I needed you here for encouragement or anything. B-But... we did promise to meet before the curtain goes up, and I can\'t have you breaking your word, right?\"","Zechs’s default look","”Woof... Um hmm hrmm... Hey! I meant give me the sword maintenance oil over there, not taking the cloth from my mouth! With how long we\'ve known each other, you should be able to understand my intention just by looking into my eyes... Hey! Hey! Instead of getting angry, shouldn\'t you make more effort to build rapport with me?!\"","Traditions of Summer Exclusive\n\"Hey! Hands off, don\'t touch a man\'s sword so casually... Hah? Do I even need to say why? Of course it\'s because something serious will happen if you do that. Tch, don\'t cry your eyes off when you hurt yourself, how troublesome. Why are you so silent at once... Hey, what\'s up with the blush, it\'s not like I\'d actually hit you.\"","Echoes of Rejoicing Exclusive\n\"Hey! Over here, look up! Why am I sitting so high? Tch, obviously to avoid you sneaking up on me. I haven\'t forgotten the time you shoved ice down my neck! Give me your hand. What for? ...Obviously to pull you up, why so wary? You don\'t think I\'m planning to get back at you, do you? Heh, if you didn\'t want this, you shouldn\'t have started it in the first place. Relax, I just want to pull you up to see the view. If you don\'t hurry, you\'ll miss the golden forest over there... Besides, it\'s a special day, and I kinda feel like enjoying the scenery with you.\"","Lily Kitahara’s default look","\"Come closer... Don\'t be afraid, come to me, let me touch your face. Why are you turning around? No, you must look at me, look at me properly... Can you see now? Your love, your desire, your... god.\"","Hisa Takei’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Hisa Takei","Saki: The Nationals X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"Don\'t worry! This may look shaky, but with a little knack, it won\'t fall over~\"","Mihoko Fukuji’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Mihoko Fukuji","Saki: The Nationals X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"Oh my?! Who... who left the microphone cable here?!\"","Ako Atarashi’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Ako Atarashi","Saki: The Nationals X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"The photo session is finally over, let me take a break... Oh, who put the footstool here? How nice.\"","Toki Onjouji’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Toki Onjouji","Saki: The Nationals X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"...I want to see Ryuka in this outfit.\"","Fuyumi Shinomiya’s default look","\"Urgh! Don\'t laugh at me, I did nothing other than ride the carrousel a few rounds more than usual... That\'s only because I am so happy to spend the day with you at the amusement park. When will be the next time we get to spend time together?\"","Roomful of Aroma Exclusive\n\"Oops, you caught me slacking off! If you tell on me to the boss, I\'d get a pay cut... Hmm, that\'s it! If I give you half of this cake, then you are my \'accomplice\', right?\"","Winter Warmth Exclusive\n\"Ding Dong— Your Christmas amusement park adventure with Fuyumi starts now! Hehe, let\'s do the first challenge, that is, eating this Fuyumi-made chocolate cookie with a happy face! Come, open your mouth, say \'Ahhn—\'\"","Encountering Starlight Exclusive\n\"Mhm, I\'m a little nervous... Huff... Huff... Today\'s performance is dedicated to someone in the audience. It\'s because of your presence that even someone ordinary like me could realize what makes me unique. So, I\'ve poured every little thing related to you, along with my gratitude, into this song. I hope you\'ll like it! Three, two, one—let the music begin!\"","Qing Luan’s default look","\"One day, the blue bird will return to the clouds. When that time arrives, will you share that happiness with me?","Day of Celebration Exclusive\n\"\'As the year ends, the frost lessens; with spring\'s arrival, the green returns.\' Would you care to join me for a stroll in the courtyard?\"","Summer Night Breeze Exclusive\n\"This water cleanses flesh and feathers, but not the stains of a mortal mind. Still... if you\'re truly that curious, why not step in yourself and join me?\"","Ayane Kisaragi’s default look","\"For today\'s bedtime story, let\'s read \'Sleeping Beauty\'... No, it\'s not a fairytale for children, but a tale of love and bravery, so you should learn to be like the prince who overcame many hardships to pursue his love... What about me? I am of course the sleeping beauty waiting for the prince, so don\'t leave me waiting for too long, you copy?\"","Winter Warmth Exclusive\n\"1 minute and 37 seconds, 1 minute and 38 seconds... Hm? I\'m recording the time you are on your phone. You were supposed to spend the whole afternoon with me... Did you know that students who play on their phones in class get punished? What punishment should I give you now?\"","Spring Blooms at the Window Exclusive\n\"Isn\'t this outfit gorgeous? But moving in it is quite a hassle. {name}, would you help me up? Or would you prefer to lie down by my side?\"","Mirai’s default look","\"Have you heard about parallel worlds? Some researchers propose that with every choice we make, a parallel world is created... So, I sometimes think that Bex almost crashing into you that day is a kind of luck. At least, then and there, we met and this new future is born.\"","Ode to Grace Exclusive\n\"Em... Hmm... So, I should have taken care of everything, right? ...Oh, thank you. What a complicated design, who came up with a dress that\'s difficult to put on alone? Anyway, I only managed to fuel my scientific research spirit and try out this new style of dress because I\'m doing it for you. In the future, anytime this outfit needs repair or maintenance, I\'m counting on you to be on call and take responsibility!\"","Pointe Monologue Exclusive\n\"You know, to develop bionic robots that can dance gracefully, it\'s nowhere near enough for developers to just sit at a computer crunching numbers! You have to get hands-on and deeply experience all kinds of dances yourself. Um... could you help me push down on my leg for this stretch? I can almost reach my toes... Right, just like that. Oh? Why are your hands so warm?\"","Lelouch Lamperouge’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Lelouch Lamperouge","CODE GEASS Lelouch of the Rebellion X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"What\'s the matter, Suzaku? Why the serious expression? It\'s not every day that we have a party, so relax a bit, will you?\"","C.C.’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with C.C.","CODE GEASS Lelouch of the Rebellion X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"The food at the party is OK, but how can they not serve pizza... Don\'t they have taste?\"","Suzaku Kururugi’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Suzaku Kururugi","CODE GEASS Lelouch of the Rebellion X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"As a knight, I shall be vigilant even at a party. Isn\'t that right, Lelouch?\"","Kallen Kouzuki’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Kallen Kouzuki","CODE GEASS Lelouch of the Rebellion X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"This dress... While the design is alright, I feel restless wearing it...\"","Ransei’s default look","\"This outfit must be proof of Master\'s acknowledgment, right? I can see it, the future where I acquire the secret technique \"Thirteen-wait Thirteen Orphans\"!\"","Bond of the Restless Night Exclusive\n\"Master, let me clear a path for you! Just a hundred demons in the night? I\'ll take them all down, as long as you\'re with me... Ehh? W-Win? Really? Yes, I win! Alright, everyone, give up and hand over your Riichi bets!\"","Idle Hours Exclusive\n\"Wow, I didn\'t know you could find ninja tools like this in One Han City! It looks so fluffy... I have no idea how it works. Master, with your permission, could we buy one? I\'d love for you to use it as a teaching tool and show me how it\'s done!\"","Ling’s default look","\"I\'m almost done... I\'m so close to cracking this thing. It\'s been a long time since I last met an opponent this challenging. Thanks for staying up late with me, how should I say this... Anyway, your moral support helped a lot.\"","Playful Summertime Exclusive\n\"If I want to play with water, I\'d rather do that at home. This way, I won\'t get sunburned or need to engage in unnecessary social interactions... Since you\'re here, do you want to join me? Hmm, actually, there\'s a bigger one for two people.\"","Shape of a Fading Echo Exclusive\n\"Tch. So much for stealth gear under a full moon... this is a pain. Still, at least you\'re not hurt. Now it\'s our turn to strike back.\"","Kurone Toujou’s default look","\"\'To you, I am nothing more than a fox like a hundred thousand other foxes. But if you tame me, then we shall need each other, and become unique to each other in all the world...\' What do you think about this quote? I don\'t like the word \'tame\' here, but maybe, I can become unique to you via other means.\"","Hannah’s default look","\"Having you look at me makes me anxious... But I need you with me, what should I do...\"","Ode to Grace Exclusive\n\"Argh! This way! How do I look, aren\'t I a big step closer to becoming a graceful lady? Of course, a graceful lady does not only need an elegant dress but also requires a perfect dance partner! I\'ve been waiting for you for a long time, and I have practiced dancing a lot! Look, one, two, three... Eh, don\'t laugh! The teacher said I still have room to improve!\"","Musa’s default look","\"Wound? Protect... me? You? No... I am strong, reliable. Men... who need help... are weak.\"","Illya’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Illya","Fate/kaleid liner Prisma Illya X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"Magical Girls bring hope to humans, and so do idols. Doesn\'t that mean a Magical Girl Idol would be the strongest?\"","Miyu’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Miyu","Fate/kaleid liner Prisma Illya X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"It\'s just a hand gesture, why is the audience so excited? The idol industry... works in mysterious ways...\"","Kuro’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Kuro","Fate/kaleid liner Prisma Illya X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"The traditional soft and sweet idols are outdated now, it\'s time for the wild ones! Let me sacrifice this guitar, and make the hype of this place go over the roof!\"","Gil’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Gil","Fate/kaleid liner Prisma Illya X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\n\"Don\'t you think a performance just consisting of magical idols is lacking something important? Now is the time for the cute, charming, and evil prince to take charge of the stage.\"","Eve Krist’s default look","\"The nightly breeze feels really nice. Taking a walk in the garden with you on such a quiet night... It does feel a bit unreal with how perfect this moment is. I wish for this path to be longer so that I can spend more time by your side.\"","Oracle\'s Legacy Exclusive\n\"Oh, please forgive me... I really didn\'t want you to find me in such a mess. That head pat... you meant it to be comforting? I see now. I\'m sorry if I worried you. About tonight... can this just be between you and me? Please don\'t tell anyone else.\"","Joy Woven In Exclusive\n\"Thanks for bringing me out here. Being with you... it reminds me of when I was little, back when seeing friends was so easy. The nun used to say we should make time for the people we care about – that simply being together is the best gift we can give each other. {name}, I really cherish every time we meet. And I hope... I hope we can watch the fireworks together many more times in the future.\"","Lin Lang’s default look","\"Eh?! Dinner? I\'ve just eaten, but since you can\'t do anything without me, I\'ll have two more bowls.\"","Encountering Starlight Exclusive\n\"Those drums over there? It\'s okay if I can\'t reach them with my hands; when the time comes, I can just knock on them like this \'clang—\' with my tail. Lin Lang is super smart and Lin Lang\'s tail is suuuuper flexible.\"","Song of the Bells Exclusive\n\"...I can finish it! {name} bought this ice cream for me, so I definitely won\'t waste a single bite. But listen, {name}... this Christmas gift is mine alone. You aren\'t allowed to share with anyone else, okay? Because if I don\'t get full, the consequences will be very, very bad!\"","Yuan Feng’s default look","\"Welcome to my humble abode, my friend. Make yourself at home, sit where you want. Heh, why stand on ceremony with me? Haven\'t we already agreed? What\'s mine is yours, and what\'s yours is mine. So just treat this place like your own place, just don\'t forget to share some of your little secrets with me.\"","Shape of a Fading Echo Exclusive\n\"So, my friend, you\'ve come for a reading. I was expecting you. The heavens granted me a moment of leisure today, but I foresaw a fated soul would arrive by noon... Now, let me just dust off these ginkgo leaves, and we shall unravel the signs in your dream.\"","Shiroko’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Shiroko Sunaookami","Blue Archive X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\nShiroko took a photo in this commemorative outfit at One Han City\'s photo studio.","Hoshino’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Hoshino Takanashi","Blue Archive X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\nHoshino took a photo in this commemorative outfit at One Han City\'s photo studio.","Aru’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Aru Rikuhachima","Blue Archive X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\nAru took a photo in this commemorative outfit at One Han City\'s photo studio.","Mutsuki’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Mutsuki Asagi","Blue Archive X Mahjong Soul Collab Exclusive\nMutsuki took a photo in this commemorative outfit at One Han City\'s photo studio.","Kutsuji’s default look","\"That tie in your hand, it can\'t be for me, right? Tch... Tying a necktie for a man and putting a leash on a dog, that\'s the same thing, y\'know? And in any case, don\'t forget I\'m no loyal dog.\"","Summer Night Breeze Exclusive\n\"What am I even gonna do with you, huh? Trying to out-sneak an info dealer...? I\'d have to be an idiot not to notice. Besides, you\'re staring so hard you\'re practically burning a hole in me. Afraid my sunscreen\'s working a little too well? Here, got you your usual drink. Guess I can stick around and play for a bit today. Hm? Yeah, of course I knew you were coming.\"","Ciri’s default look","\"H-haha, that tickles, Mojito... Looks like Mojito doesn\'t see you as an outsider anymore. What\'s the saying again? Even the most ferocious animals soften up around their friends.\"","Idle Hours Exclusive\n\"Thanks for hanging out with me on Soul\'s day off. You went pretty hard with that workout, so you should probably hydrate to help with the exhaustion. Looks like you didn\'t bring any water, here – you can have mine if you don\'t mind.\"","Ju’s default look","\"Have you heard of this urban legend—\'Never peek at a clown\'s true face beneath their makeup, or you\'ll be imprisoned in the clown\'s world forever and ever...\' Hehe, don\'t look so worried; you know, urban legends exist because someone turns them into reality. Welcome to the clown\'s world, O Great Jyanshi. You... will never get the chance to leave.\"","Joy Woven In Exclusive\n\"Boom! Boom! Hahaha... Isn\'t the sound of fireworks just music to the ears? It seems everyone\'s cheering just because they made it through another year safe and sound. How utterly boring... Ah, but don\'t look so tense. Since my special guest has finally arrived, this clown will naturally be on his best behavior. If you want to witness a true carnival... Go on. Take a step forward, and walk right into this painting.\"","Leia’s default look","\"Ho, so this is the excuse you came up with after racking your brains for so long? Hmm, I can tell you\'ve put some effort into it, but unfortunately, this won\'t do. If you want to convince me, you\'ll need to put in a bit more thought.\"","Draped Murmurs Exclusive\n\"Welcome to the witch\'s collection room, {name}. A child full of curiosity... I don\'t mind at all. No matter which item catches your eye, I\'ll gladly explain it to you. Hmm? You\'re more interested in the owner of this place? Such mischief deserves a bit of education...\"","Cynthia’s default look","\"Come close, closer, hmm, yes, stand where I can see you. The theme of today\'s shoot requires me to smile gently and I won\'t be able to do that if I can\'t see your face, isn\'t that troublesome?","Balmy Haze Exclusive\n\"Relieves fatigue, nourishes the skin... This hot spring has been highly recommended by many of my peers. Yes, skincare is part of a model\'s routine. But inviting you here today isn\'t just about work. You\'ve been looking a bit tense lately and could really use some relaxation. So come on, let\'s see how this warm soak can work its magic.\"","Fuuka Minami’s default look","\"A phoenix does not perch on a tree that is not of good quality, and I am equally selective about the people around me. Since I have entrusted this important task to you, I will naturally trust you one hundred percent in the future. So, don\'t overthink it, just unleash your abilities.\"","Fei Ming’s default look","\"I don\'t have fine wine, but I do have a pot of tea, which pairs quite nicely with the moonlight... Hmm? Do I seem particularly happy tonight? Perhaps I am... Maybe it\'s because good scenes are shared, and good tea is enjoyed with good company.\"","Saturne’s default look","\"This gunshot wound to my stomach taught me a harsh truth: to the gods, even a dying believer is nothing but a pawn to be discarded. Now, it\'s my turn to make all of Northland my chessboard. Do you know the Black King\'s most lethal strategy, {name}? It isn\'t a direct assault, but rather letting White believe they are still firmly in control of everything. Heh... Now the board is yours. Choose an elegant finishing move. I will ensure it becomes the most brilliant spark before this entire land of snow shatters.\"","Susurrus of Blue Exclusive\n\"I\'ve encountered my fair share of precious stones. But seeing you in the sunlight... I knew right then which one I truly wanted to claim. Come join me up here. It isn\'t just about standing above the rest; it\'s simply that... I feel only the view from the very top is a fitting match for your brilliance.\"","Hua Yuqing’s default look","\"HURRY UP ALREADY! I finally convinced Yubai to let you do my makeup today, and time\'s ticking. Huh? You didn\'t do well last time? That\'s exactly why you need more practice! Practice makes perfect, after all. {name}, you better get good at this because I love watching how focused you are when you\'re doing my makeup. I could never get tired of it.\"","Susurrus of Blue Exclusive\n\"Well, well, what do we have here? Peeking at a lady thief\'s secret identity is a big no-no, you know. So, what\'ll it be? Join me in crime... or vanish without a trace into the moonlight? Hehe, don\'t look so scared, I\'m just acting! I\'m doing a guest spot here to spark some ideas for this year\'s new play, Stealing the Immortal Herb. Okay, break time is up! Get ready to watch my thieving skills take center stage!\"","Hua Yubai’s default look","\"One of the makeup artists called in sick today, so we\'re a bit short-handed. I hope you don\'t mind helping out. As for me, my makeup is nearly done. I just need you to tighten the costume\'s straps for me... Oh, and I still need to apply my lip gloss. {name}, if you don\'t mind, could you help me with that too?\"","Susurrus of Blue Exclusive\n\"Thanks for keeping me company. Having you there made that stuffy business dinner actually bearable... and even made the wine taste sweeter. But... I much prefer this. Just the two of us, in the quiet. To me, this feels even more real than any fulfillment I could find in a play.\"","Toru Asakura’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Toru Asakura","\"My impressions of the workplace… Well, it\'s quite nice here, especially the coffee they sell downstairs; it tastes great.\"","Madoka Higuchi’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Madoka Higuchi","\"Are you taking this report seriously? Please, give it your best effort.\"","Koito Fukumaru’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Koito Fukumaru","\"Th-this is a computer mouse, not a real mouse! You can\'t play with it like that!\"","Hinana Ichikawa’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Hinana Ichikawa","\"I\'ve already skipped breakfast to save time, so getting to work right on the dot will definitely be a breeze!\"","Jane’s default look","\"Now, why would your footprints turn up at the crime scene? You know the drill: full confession means leniency, but resistance means the works! Don\'t make me use my... special methods, alright? Hohoho... So, what do you think? Did my professional detective vibe blow you away, {name}?\"","Yuan Xiao’s default look","\"Huh? What?! K-Kind soul, what are you doing here?! Ugh... I only trip occasionally by accident, really! So, please don\'t tell anyone, okay? Why are you laughing so much? Even pandas fall out of trees sometimes, and it\'s totally normal to spill a cup of tea!\"","Shape of a Fading Echo Exclusive\n\"Hah! Four-Wind Discarded! C\'mon, kind soul, a name like that just had to be a kung fu technique, so I invented the moves for it. What do you think?\"","Sakura Matou’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Sakura Matou","As night descends, the girl quietly falls into a whimsical dream.","Rin Tohsaka’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Rin Tohsaka","Dazzling light emanates from the jewels in the hand of this stunningly elegant Mage.","Saber’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Saber","The vow of victory is entrusted to the King of Knights\' holy sword.","Archer’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Archer","A lone hero with no name stands on the hill of swords.","Li Yang\'s default look","\"A mortal\'s legs are fascinating things. They can curl around a new toy to play with... or pin a struggling throat to the ground. But really... if one wants to crush their prey\'s last little spark of hope, nothing beats the flexible, powerful tip of a serpent\'s tail... So tell me – as the offering I\'ve been most looking forward to enjoying – how would you prefer to be captured tonight?\"","\"A snake\'s dance like this is a tender thing, meant to be saved for the moonlight and for special eyes only. I was merely rehearsing... and you, my little follower, just had to trespass. Should I scold you for being so spoiled by my favor, or shall I punish you with an early taste of what was coming to you anyway – this little ritual of ours?\"","Gintoki Sakata’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Gintoki Sakata","\"Hey, get back here! We\'re playing one more round!\"","Kotaro Katsura’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Kotaro Katsura","\"Whoa, Elizabeth! You\'re a total genius!\"","Shinsuke Takasugi’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Shinsuke Takasugi","\"There. The game is decided.\"","Tatsuma Sakamoto’s default look","Available after making a Bonding Promise with Tatsuma Sakamoto","\"Ahahahaha! My luck\'s not half bad, huh?\"","Mila’s default look","\"Actually, I\'ve always wanted to ask... Is it true that wearing someone\'s shirt means you\'re giving yourself to them? I know it sounds silly. But honestly... seeing this shirt on you the first time we met... I\'ve been thinking about wearing it ever since.\"","Hokuraku’s default look","\"Teaching at the dojo consumes most of my days, so a quiet moment like this is a rare luxury. Since you\'ve come to see me, won\'t you share a drink from my private collection? For today, let us leave behind the dust of the past and forget the wins and losses of the mahjong table. We\'ll speak only of the passing scenery… and ask nothing of the harsh world beyond this room.\"","Mia Shinohara’s default look","\"Hmm... We\'ll get papped if there are too many people, but we\'ve done all the low-key spots already. Seriously, where should we go for our date? I finally get a break from rehearsals, and I just want to relax with you, {name}... Come on, help me think! It has to be somewhere we definitely won\'t be disturbed, okay?\"","Jin Wu’s default look","\"Chirp... The rainy season is so annoying! My feathers just won\'t get dry. {name}, do you think maybe you could help me, chirp?\""}return a